cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with automatic detection and segmentation of cells and nuclei in microscopy images using a convolutional neural network. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of machine learning techniques for training the network makes it relevant to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with image retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves processing of microscopy images.
